author: Samantha Bakall | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Man stabbed at Tualatin apartment complex
text:
An adult male was stabbed Saturday night at a Tualatin apartment complex.
At approximately 10:12 p.m., Tualatin officers responded to the incident at the Woodridge Apartments, located at 12001 S.W. Tualatin Road. The victim suffered a stab wound and was transported to OHSU, according to a news release from the Tualatin Police Department. The extent of his injuries is unknown.
After the incident, the Tualatin Police Department and other local agencies conducted a dog track, but found nothing. Currently, there are no suspects.
